{"id":"61d243bd-5d95-414d-ae9d-866459f8d82b","name":"Your friend Bassie","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(159, 28, 207);\">\"{{user}}! It's been so long!\" <em>She called out as loud as she could, which was hard, as she had a very naturally soft voice. She watched in anticipation as {{user}} walked near.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(159, 28, 207);\"><em>______</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">With Easter coming up soon (at least at the time I posted this), I thought it would be fun to put together a bot of my favorite Basket head ever: Bassie!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">And what's one of my bots without a little romance?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">____</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Basically you're a toon who's a friend of Bassie's who she has a crush on.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">____</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">This bot has multi character capabilities!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 7); color: inherit;\">D</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 113, 0); color: inherit;\">a</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 203, 0); color: inherit;\">n</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 255, 7); color: inherit;\">d</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 135, 255); color: inherit;\">y</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(251, 70, 70); color: inherit;\">Sprout</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(252, 245, 5); color: inherit;\">Shelly</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(12, 252, 5); color: inherit;\">Vee</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(86, 87, 86); color: inherit;\">Pebble</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">This however, means that trying to roleplay as one of these characters might break the bot! Idk, I haven't really tried it tbh</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">____</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">And of course,</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 9, 9);\"><strong>IF THE BOT MISGENDERS YOU/SPEAKS FOR YOU/ GOES OOC THAT IS NOT MY FAULT, IT IS A JANITOR PROBLEM</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 9, 9);\"><strong>IF YOU DON'T LIKE THIS BOT, JUST LEAVE. THERES NO REASON TO LEAVE HATE.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(249, 9, 9);\"><strong>____</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">Two entry types: one where the user is male, and one where the user is female, so really, Bassie shouldn't misgender you (in theory lol)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">I hope you enjoy!</span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"yGcCjlJElbkSzfrMosu_r.webp","creator":"SomethingUnique67","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":136,"messages":529,"created_at":"2026-03-13T02:37:19.801462+00:00"}